Comment: 0,0:22:12.82,0:22:20.58,RMLyrics2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}koi-suru hima mo nai yo  nami ga oshiyosete-kuru
Comment: 0,0:22:20.74,0:22:28.79,RMLyrics2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}kioku no naka o oyoide mo  genjitsu wa  cool and dry
Comment: 0,0:22:28.88,0:22:36.51,RMLyrics2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}sore o tashikametakute  doko ni samayoi-yuku no
Comment: 0,0:22:36.76,0:22:44.02,RMLyrics2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}to'oi kumo no you ni  tsukamenai anata ni
Comment: 0,0:22:44.18,0:22:51.86,RMLyrics2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}tsuite-yuku  doko-made mo  kokoro ni chikatte
Comment: 0,0:22:52.02,0:22:55.78,RMLyrics2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}itsuka subete ga wakatte mo
Comment: 0,0:22:55.91,0:22:59.83,RMLyrics2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}anata o suki de irareru-koto
Comment: 0,0:22:59.95,0:23:07.63,RMLyrics2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}tatoe tatakau mainichi ni  akekurete mo
Comment: 0,0:23:07.75,0:23:15.47,RMLyrics2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}natsukashisa de omo'u furusato  mukashi no jibun utsusu
Comment: 0,0:23:15.59,0:23:24.73,RMLyrics2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}hikari to kage no roman  oikakete
Comment: 0,0:22:04.97,0:22:08.70,TLLyrics2,,0,0,0,,The twilight would know no weariness
Comment: 0,0:22:08.82,0:22:12.70,TLLyrics2,,0,0,0,,If we talked about romance all night long
Comment: 0,0:22:12.82,0:22:20.58,TLLyrics2,,0,0,0,,There's no time to love, the waves are surging this way
Comment: 0,0:22:20.74,0:22:28.79,TLLyrics2,,0,0,0,,Even as I swim in my memories, reality is cool and dry
Comment: 0,0:22:28.88,0:22:36.51,TLLyrics2,,0,0,0,,Where will I wander to make sure of that love?
Comment: 0,0:22:36.76,0:22:44.02,TLLyrics2,,0,0,0,,You're like an unattainable, far-away cloud
Comment: 0,0:22:44.18,0:22:51.86,TLLyrics2,,0,0,0,,Yet I shall follow you wherever you go, I swear on my heart
Comment: 0,0:22:52.02,0:22:59.83,TLLyrics2,,0,0,0,,Even if you find out someday and realize that I can love you
Comment: 0,0:22:59.95,0:23:07.63,TLLyrics2,,0,0,0,,Even if we spend our days constantly fighting
Comment: 0,0:23:07.75,0:23:15.47,TLLyrics2,,0,0,0,,Picturing my old self, I recalled my hometown fondly
Comment: 0,0:23:15.59,0:23:24.73,TLLyrics2,,0,0,0,,Chasing the romance of light and shadow
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.96,0:23:35.29,Narration,,0,0,0,,ما هو ذلك؟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.03,0:23:38.63,Narration,,0,0,0,,!انظر هناك
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.63,0:23:39.83,Narration,,0,0,0,,ما الامر؟
